Hannah Rae https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hannah_Rae 0 Hannah Rae is an English actress. She came to prominence in her 2016 feature film debut City of Tiny Lights, for which she was nominated for the Most Promising Newcomer Award at the British Independent Film Awards.
